Introduction

T5 (Korean: 티5; Japanese: ティー5) is a 5-member sub-unit of the boy group, TREASURE under YG Entertainment. The members are JIHOON, JUNKYU, JAEHYUK, DOYOUNG, and JUNGHWAN.
